An inmate serving a life sentence collapsed and died at Naivasha GK prison on Wednesday.The prisoner, who had been jailed for robbery with violence, was confirmed dead upon arrival at the facility's health center.A source at the prison said he had complained of chest pain.&ldquo;The inmate who was transferred from Kamiti had health issues and was on medication,&rdquo; the source said.Patrick Mwenda, the officer in charge of the prison, said a post mortem will reveal the cause of death.He said the body was taken to Naivasha hospital mortuary.